8 COUNTY.
9 (2) THE PART OF THE SURCHARGE COLLECTED UNDER SUBSECTION
10 (A) OF THIS SECTION THAT IS ATTRIBUTABLE TO THE RATE GREATER THAN 6%
11 SHALL BE DISTRIBUTED TO THE GENERAL FUND OF THE COUNTY.
